      "text": "Issues\n[MIS LOG IN](#)\n[![Electric Reliability Council of Texas](https://www.ercot.com/files/assets/2023/07/14/ERCOT-logo-122x45.svg \"ERCOT home\")](https://www.ercot.com)\n* [Home](https://www.ercot.com/)\n* [Market Rules](https://www.ercot.com/mktrules)\n* Issues\n## OBDRR040\n* [Summary](#summary)\n* [Action](#action)\n* [Voting Record](#votingrecord)\n* [Background](#background)\n* [Key Documents](#keydocs)\n#### Summary\n|Title|**ORDC Changes Related to NPRR1131, Controllable Load Participation in Non-Spin**|\nNext Group||\nNext Step||\nStatus|Approved on 09/15/2022|\n#### Action\n|Date|Gov Body|Action Taken|Next steps|\n[09/15/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/09152022-PUCT-Meeting)|[PUCT](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=puct)|[Approved](#votingrecord)||\n[08/16/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/08162022-Board-of-Directors-Meeting)|[BOARD](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=board)|[Recommended for Approval](#votingrecord)|PUCT for consideration|\n[06/27/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/06272022-TAC-Meeting)|[TAC](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=tac)|[Recommended for Approval](#votingrecord)|Board for consideration|\n[05/25/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/05252022-TAC-Meeting)|[TAC](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=tac)|[Deferred/Tabled](#votingrecord)|TAC for consideration|\n#### Voting Record\n|Date|Gov Body|Motion|Result|\n[09/15/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/09152022-PUCT-Meeting)|[PUCT](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=puct)|To approve OBDRR040 and accompanying ERCOT Market Impact Statement as presented in Project No. 52934, Review of Rules Adopted by the Independent Organization|Passed|\n[08/16/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/08162022-Board-of-Directors-Meeting)|[BOARD](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=board)|To recommend approval of OBDRR040 as recommended by TAC in the 6/27/22 TAC Report|Passed|\n[06/27/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/06272022-TAC-Meeting)|[TAC](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=tac)|To recommend approval of OBDRR040 as submitted and the 4/25/22 Impact Analysis|Passed|\n[05/25/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/05252022-TAC-Meeting)|[TAC](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=tac)|To table OBDRR040|Passed|\n#### Background\n|Status:|Approved|\nDate Posted:|Apr 25, 2022|\nSponsor:|ERCOT|\nUrgent:|No|\nSections:|Methodology for Implementing Operating Reserve Demand Curve (ORDC) to Calculate Real-Time Reserve Price Adder|\nDescription:|This Other Binding Document Revision Request (OBDRR) removes the Controllable Load Resource providing Non-Spinning Reserve (Non-Spin) schedules and Regulation Service schedules from the capacity calculations in alignment with NPRR1131 as a standing deployment.|\nReason:|Meets Strategic goals / Market efficiencies or enhancements|\n#### Key Documents\n[040OBDRR-01 ORDC Changes Related to NPRR1131, Controllable Load Participation in Non-Spin 042522]()\nApr 25, 2022 - docx - 81.1 KB\n[040OBDRR-02 Impact Analysis 042522]()\nApr 25, 2022 - docx - 31.1 KB\n[040OBDRR-03 TAC Ballot 052522]()\nMay 31, 2022 - xls - 140 KB\n[040OBDRR-04 TAC Report 052522]()\nMay 31, 2022 - docx - 82 KB\n[040OBDRR-05 TAC Ballot 062722]()\nJun 28, 2022 - xls - 140 KB\n[040OBDRR-06 TAC Report 062722]()\nJun 28, 2022 - docx - 82.3 KB\n[040OBDRR-07 Board Report 081622]()\nAug 16, 2022 - docx - 82.5 KB\n[040OBDRR-08 PUCT Report 091522]()\nSep 19, 2022 - docx - 81.6 KB\n##### Related Content\n###### On this site\n* [Market Rules](https://www.ercot.com/mktrules)\n* [Other Binding Documents Revision Requests](https://www.ercot.com/mktrules/issues/obdrr)\nERCOT-Lockup-white",
