 2 \n4.2.1 Operating Condition Notice ... 2 \n4.2.2 Advisory ... 3 \n4.2.3 Watch ... 5 \n4.2.4 Emergency Notice ... 6 \n\nERCOT NODAL OPERATING GUIDES – FEBRUARY 1, 2022 4 \n4.3 Operation to Maintain Transmission System Security ... 7 \n4.3.1 Real-Time and Short Term Planning ... 7 \n4.4 Block Load Transfers between ERCOT and Non-ERCOT System ... 7 \n4.5 Energy Emergency Alert (EEA) ... 8 \n4.5.1 General ... 8 \n4.5.2 Operating Procedures ... 8 \n4.5.3 Implementation ... 10 \n4.5.3.1 General Procedures Prior to EEA Operations ... 12 \n4.5.3.2 General Procedures During EEA Operations ... 12 \n4.5.3.3 EEA Levels ... 13 \n4.5.3.4 Load Shed Obligation………………………………………………………………..20 \n4.5.3.5 EEA Termination…………………………………………...……………………….21 \n4.6 Black Start Service ... 22 \n4.6.1 Principles ... 22 \n4.6.2 Strategies ... 23 \n4.6.3 Priorities ... 23 \n4.6.4 Responsibilities ... 24 \n4.6.5 Black Start Emergency Back Up Communication Facilities Criteria ... 28 \n4.7 Geomagnetic Disturbance Operating Plan ... 28 \n4.7.1 Monitoring and Dissemination of Space Weather Information ... 28 \n4.7.2 Development and Submission of TO GMD Operating Procedures or Processes ... 28 \n4.7.3 ERCOT’s GMD Operating Plan and ERCOT Review of TO GMD Operating Procedures or \nProcesses ... 29 \n4.8 Responsive Reserve Service During Scarcity Conditions…………………………………………30 \n4.8.1 Responsive Reserve Service Manual Deployment…………………………………………..30 \n4.8.2 Responsive Reserve Service Manual Recall…….……….………….………………………31 \n5 Network Operations Modeling Requirements ... 1 \n5.1 System Modeling Information ... 1 \n6 Disturbance Monitoring and System Protection ... 1 \n6.1 Disturbance Monitoring Requirements ... 1 \n6.1.1 Introduction ... 1 \n6.1.2 Fault Recording and Sequence of Events Recording Equipment ... 1 \n6.1.2.1 Fault Recording Requirements ... 2 \n6.1.2.2 Fault Recording and Sequence of Events Recording Equipment Location \nRequirements ... 2 \n6.1.2.3 Fault Recording and Sequence of Events Recording Data Requirements ... 3 \n6.1.2.4 Fault Recording and Sequence of Events Recording Data Retention and Reporting \nRequirements ... 4 \n6.1.3 Phasor Measurement Recording Equipment Inclu",
