r/06272022-TAC-Meeting)|[TAC](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=tac)|To recommend approval of OBDRR040 as submitted and the 4/25/22 Impact Analysis|Passed|\n[05/25/2022](https://www.ercot.com/calendar/05252022-TAC-Meeting)|[TAC](https://www.ercot.com/widgets/committee?find=tac)|To table OBDRR040|Passed|\n#### Background\n|Status:|Approved|\nDate Posted:|Apr 25, 2022|\nSponsor:|ERCOT|\nUrgent:|No|\nSections:|Methodology for Implementing Operating Reserve Demand Curve (ORDC) to Calculate Real-Time Reserve Price Adder|\nDescription:|This Other Binding Document Revision Request (OBDRR) removes the Controllable Load Resource providing Non-Spinning Reserve (Non-Spin) schedules and Regulation Service schedules from the capacity calculations in alignment with NPRR1131 as a standing deployment.|\nReason:|Meets Strategic goals / Market efficiencies or enhancements|\n#### Key Documents\n[040OBDRR-01 ORDC Changes Related to NPRR1131, Controllable Load Participation in Non-Spin 042522]()\nApr 25, 2022 - docx - 81.1 KB\n[040OBDRR-02 Impact Analysis 042522]()\nApr 25, 2022 - docx - 31.1 KB\n[040OBDRR-03 TAC Ballot 052522]()\nMay 31, 2022 - xls - 140 KB\n[040OBDRR-04 TAC Report 052522]()\nMay 31, 2022 - docx - 82 KB\n[040OBDRR-05 TAC Ballot 062722]()\nJun 28, 2022 - xls - 140 KB\n[040OBDRR-06 TAC Report 062722]()\nJun 28, 2022 - docx - 82.3 KB\n[040OBDRR-07 Board Report 081622]()\nAug 16, 2022 - docx - 82.5 KB\n[040OBDRR-08 PUCT Report 091522]()\nSep 19, 2022 - docx - 81.6 KB\n##### Related Content\n###### On this site\n* [Market Rules](https://www.ercot.com/mktrules)\n* [Other Binding Documents Revision Requests](https://www.ercot.com/mktrules/issues/obdrr)\nERCOT-Lockup-white",
